Program: The Forum
Title: 05/07/2009: Part 1
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p003jj0h
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 6 Jul 2009
Listen here for Part 1 THE FORUM, the ideas programme with BRIDGET KENDALL. Physicist FRANK WILCZEK on why space isn’t really empty. Writer and activist ARUNDHATI ROY on why India’s democracy doesn’t help the masses. Philosopher SUSAN NEIMAN on a new Enlightenment.